text: Anachevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Andreyevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 324 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo, 2 km from Andreyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Anachevo
